{"tid":1841971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】《WSJ》引述消息人士 稱美將派包機撤困武漢國民","createTime":"2020-01-25T12:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T14:53:05.000Z","uid":30040,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"1356ee3fb0a3a92deee3ffc5069773c356d4d9b8","tid":1841971,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:53:09.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續惡化，武漢陷入封鎖狀態，美國《華爾街日報》引述消息人士稱，美方正安排包機，計劃在周日撤走被困武漢的美國公民和外交人員。<br />\n報道引述消息人士指，現時武漢約有1,000名美國公民，美國駐武漢總領事館正接觸他們，讓他們可以乘搭專機離開武漢，但他們須自行承擔相關的費用。<br />\n報道指，美方近日與中方就有關安排進行磋商，據報華府已獲中方同意進行有關行動。消息稱，美方將安排一部波音767客機前往武漢作為包機，該客機可乘搭230名乘客，機上將會有醫護人員同行。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849650de612876a72446a96ae9293d80a4a90d06","tid":1841971,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:53:45.000Z","msg":"：元得走好走"},{"pid":"3ddae7d9e8600f315f6dcd8653088dbe4590e05c","tid":1841971,"uid":50502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:55:00.000Z","msg":"方舟計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國人就封係入面自生自滅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4874b0d65a9ed4512e648b5d85d4a246f19e8d9a","tid":1841971,"uid":63651,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:55:55.000Z","msg":"好想做美帝子民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5090ad483d8efbd9077384d0c3aa750c6bbe57","tid":1841971,"uid":2267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"美國行到呢一步，即係短時間都唔會搞得掂<br />\n中国又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02171dbab389a4eb5c2eddf0f90a633acd0dbf4","tid":1841971,"u